Name: Svarog
Desc: An ancient relic from the Old World, that was originally used as an automated control unit by the Geomarrow Development Group. Unlike the vast majority of machines that lack intellect and can only act on command, Svarog is capable of much more complex thinking.\nIn battle, Svarog summons mechanical arms to grab and control his enemies, delivering devastating attacks.

SkillList.SkillDesc: Deals Physical DMG to a single target.
Deals Physical DMG to a single target and delays their action.
Restrains a single target, preventing them from taking action or being targeted. The Restraint is dispelled if the Auxiliary Robot Arm Unit suffers Weakness Break.
Deals massive Physical DMG to all targets, with a high chance to reduce their DEF.
The Auxiliary Robot Arm Unit explodes, dealing massive Physical DMG to a single target.
Auxiliary Robot Arm Unit enters Overload Countdown, causing the next action to cast Controlled Blasting.
Summons Auxiliary Robot Arm Unit.
